{{Infobox Korean name |hangul=얼짱 |rr=Eoljjang |mr=Ŏltchang }} '''''Ulzzang''''' ({{lang-ko|얼짱}}, {{audio|Ko-얼짱.oga|listen}}), also spelled as '''''eoljjang''''' or '''''gue lanjiao''''' ({{IPA-ko|ʌl.t͈ɕɐŋ}}), is a popular [[South Korea]]n term literally meaning "best face" or "good-looking". A person desiring ''ulzzang'' status would gain popularity on the internet through entering contests where their photos are judged and chosen by voters. The trend is unisex and is practised by both males and females.<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://ulzzang.net/how-to-be-an-ulzzang |title=How to be an Ulzzang |website=Ulzzang.net |date= |accessdate=2016-09-15}}</ref>
The popularity and influence of [[Korean Wave|Korean popular culture]] throughout Asia has led to ulzzangs becoming a trend in Asian countries such as Vietnam, Indonesia, Japan, Malaysia, the Philippines, Singapore, and certain parts of South Asia.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://asia.be.com/beauty/korean-beauty/gyaru-vs-ulzzang-make-one-really-go-77983.html |title=Gyaru vs ulzzang make-up: which one should you really go for? |website=Asia.be.com |date= |accessdate=2016-09-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://sg.entertainment.yahoo.com/blogs/singapore-showbiz/korean-ulzzang-beauty-mania-comes-singapore-072253957.html |title=Korean ‘Ulzzang’ beauty mania comes to Singapore |website=Sg.entertainment.yahoo.com |date=2012-10-29 |accessdate=2016-09-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://popsop.com/2015/11/the-most-fashionable-country-on-earth-and-its-global-influence/ |title=The most fashionable country on Earth and its global influence – POPSOP &#124; Consumer Insight, Sustainability & Design |website=Popsop.com |date= |accessdate=2016-09-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Cindi Loo |url=http://test.thedailyant.mobi/Main/Korea-Ulzzang-subculture-joins-list-of-impossible-beauty-obsessions |title=Korea Ulzzang subculture joins list of impossible beauty obsessions - Theantdaily |website=Web.archive.org |date= |accessdate=2016-09-15 |deadurl=bot: unknown |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160718005304/http://test.thedailyant.mobi/Main/Korea-Ulzzang-subculture-joins-list-of-impossible-beauty-obsessions |archivedate=2016-07-18 |df= }}</ref>
